# Sbuild 

Cloned version of the official package https://salsa.debian.org/debian/sbuild
but allowing network connection inside dpkg-buildpackage

## Use

```bash
git clone https://github.com/eth-pkg/sbuild.git
cd sbuild 
# install dependencies
sudo apt-get install dh-python dh-sequence-python3 libyaml-tiny-perl python3-all
# build package
dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc  
# install newly built package 
cd .. && sudo dpkg -i sbuild_0.85.6_all.deb libsbuild-perl_0.85.6_all.deb
```